FBIS4-53649 "dreas099_c_94017" FBIS-EAS-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 North Korea WPK Secretary Meets With PRC Delegation WPK Secretary Meets With PRC Delegation SK2005152594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1514 GMT 20 May 94 SK2005152594 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 20 (KCNA) -- Hwang Chang-yop, secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK], today met and had a friendly talk with the visiting delegation of the party school of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China led by Vice-president Liu Shengyu. Present on the occasion were Vice-president of Kim Il-song Higher Party School U Tal-ho and a councillor of the Chinese Embassy here.
